{"tid":248930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[蝗災來臨] 鄰國用戶解禁！朋友圈內容 可同步至FB帳戶","createTime":"2017-05-19T03:02:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T08:40:14.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4db0c299fb95c9c9c6d124e0991b732d189e2d","tid":248930,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:02:27.000Z","msg":"據《南華早報》報道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>騰訊（700）旗下的微信，最新已容許鄰國用戶，將朋友圈內容同步分享至Facebook及Twitter。</strong></span>現階段只有iOS用戶，開放相關功能，料稍後時間將覆蓋至Android用戶。<br />\n<br />\n目前Facebook月活躍用戶19.4億個，Twitter則有3.28億月活躍用戶，兩者均未能打入中國市場。<br />\n<br />\n然而由於中國仍禁止登陸兩社交平台，因此要啟動有關功能，用戶必先必先翻牆，然後將微信戶口連結Facebook及Twitter戶口。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，騰訊一直希望鞏固外國市場勢力及在華的外國人市場，今次容許將朋友圈內容同步分享至Facebook及Twitter，對騰訊有利。"},{"pid":"33983da5c6f191728515ee5f95992b8e822c3a92","tid":248930,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"青山走犯，大獲！"},{"pid":"063693c714089f509866965fcfd97b5ded07f685","tid":248930,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:12:20.000Z","msg":"只係開拓「強國以外」嘅海外市場（包括港澳臺地區）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a262d21577d76d0b89565b3dd9ff1881568a1975","tid":248930,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:13:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bff9364dcd845b98e61b2f7d7deeff0c0ebd9bb4","tid":248930,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:25:33.000Z","msg":"唔好放D生番出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2b1428cb6c11204674b458a0418e287941c072f","tid":248930,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:27:42.000Z","msg":"FB點解加新function  要有得block微信訊息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34efc782ed1384ce90e3fcb5e814caa537cd6b8d","tid":248930,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201